---
title: Cherry Tomato Gnocchi with Apple Salad & Cheddar
description: Soft pillowy bundles of potato gnocchi, smothered in cheese and baked until deliciously golden and oozy. Now, if that hasn’t got
your mouth watering, wait until you pull this dish of bubbling goodness from your oven.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-cherry-tomato-gnocchi-8c779d95.jpg
